WEBVTT

00:03.189 --> 00:06.247
In Afghanistan, a suicide bomber on a motorbike...

00:06.513 --> 00:09.991
...attacked a joint US-Afghan patrol near Bagram Airfield,...

00:10.408 --> 00:13.089
...killing six NATO soldiers and wounding three others.

00:15.917 --> 00:18.812
In China, authorities say 91 people are missing...

00:18.894 --> 00:23.680
...after a massive landslide buried an industrial park in the southern city of Shenzhen.

00:25.448 --> 00:29.607
In Belgium, police have detained five people, including two brothers,...

00:29.922 --> 00:33.855
...during a series of raids connected to last month's Paris attacks.

00:34.680 --> 00:39.750
In Spain, Prime Minister Mariano Rajoy says he has received a democratic mandate...

00:40.017 --> 00:43.607
...to try and form a government after Sunday's general election.

00:47.204 --> 00:48.576
And finally from Libya,...

00:48.807 --> 00:52.911
...two migrants drowned while more than a hundred are rescued in the Mediterranean,...

00:53.207 --> 00:56.172
...after a boat en route to Italy got into trouble.

